Iqbal - Mukta Searchlight Films - Subhash Ghai
Page 3 - Lighthouse Entertainment - Bobby Pushkarna, Kavita Pushkarna
Parineeta - Vinod Chopra Productions - Vidhu Vinod Chopra
Hazaaron Khwaishein Aisi - Pritish Nandy Communications Ltd - Rangita Pritish Nandy

2007  No award
